data.description: OPEN HOUSE Sunday 1-3. So much to offer!!! Solid and well-maintained brick and vinyl home in high demand area. A large deck at front covered entrance welcomes your guests.  Many of the original features remain along with the most important updates. Hardwood floors under carpets in most rooms.  Special features including crown molding, partial open staircase, living room fireplace w/ blower, original tile flooring in both baths and foyer. Updated kitchen has pantry with pull out shelves, newer vinyl flooring and all appliances stay. Cute space off kitchen and LR has cath. ceiling and built in shelving (great office or den).  Nicely updated half bath and many built-ins throughout the home. Spacious living room and DR w/ corner built in. Second floor holds 4 bedrooms all with hardwood floors. Master boasts Jack and Jill closets and many custom features. Nice tiled full bath.  Newer windows throughout, Central air, concrete driveway, att. 2 car garage. Basement laundry, workshop and possible finished room. Delayed negotiations... offers, if any, will be due at 1PM on Friday December 1st!
